 France squads at the [[FIFA World Cup]]s of [[1998 FIFA World Cup|1998]] and [[2002 FIFA World Cup|2002]], and [[UEFA European Championships]] in [[UEFA Euro 1996|1996]] and [[UEFA Euro 2000|2000]].]]\n\n:Source:<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/thuram-intl.html \"Lilian Thuram \u2013 Century of International Appearances\"]. ''[[Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation|RSSSF]]''. Retrieved 30 June 2012.</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|colspan=\"3\"|[[France national football team|France national team]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|1994||1||0\n|-\n|1995||5||0\n|-\n|1996||13||0\n|-\n|1997||8||0\n|-\n|1998||16||2\n|-\n|1999||9||0\n|-\n|2000||14||0\n|-\n|2001||4||0\n|-\n|2002||12||0\n|-\n|2003||12||0\n|-\n|2004||9||0\n|-\n|2005||7||0\n|-\n|2006||16||0\n|-\n|2007||10||0\n|-\n|2008||6||0\n|-\n!Total||142||2\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || rowspan=\"2\" | 8 July 1998 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Stade de France]], Saint-Denis || rowspan=\"2\" | {{fb|Croatia}} || 1\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | 2\u20131 || rowspan=\"2\" | [[1998 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n| 2. || 2\u20131\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Monaco'''<ref name=SW>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/lilian-thuram/542/|title=L. Thuram|work=Soccerway|accessdate=30 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Coupe de France]]: [[1990\u201391 Coupe de France|1990\u201391]]\n\n'''Parma'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: [[1998\u201399 Coppa Italia|1998\u201399]]\n*[[UEFA Cup]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Cup|1998\u201399]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[1999 Supercoppa Italiana|1999]]\n\n'''Juventus'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[2001\u201302 Serie A|2001\u201302]], [[2002\u201303 Serie A|2002\u201303]]\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[2002 Supercoppa Italiana|2002]], [[2003 Supercoppa Italiana|2003]]\n\n'''Barcelona'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]]: [[2006 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|2006]]\n\n'''France'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[FIFA World Cup]]: [[1998 FIFA World Cup|1998]]\n*[[UEFA European Championship]]: [[UEFA Euro 2000|2000]]\n*[[FIFA Confederations Cup]]: [[2003 FIFA Confederations Cup|2003]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[France Football#French Player of the Year|French Player of the Year]]: 1997<ref name=\"France \u2013 Footballer of the Year\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/franpoy.html |title=France \u2013 Footballer of the Year |publisher=RSSSF |date=8 Jan 2010 |accessdate=16 October 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905115225/http://rsssf.com/miscellaneous/franpoy.html |archivedate= 5 September 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[Guerin d'Oro]]: 1997<ref name=\"Guerin d'Oro\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |title=Italy \u2013 Footballer of the Year |publisher=RSSSF |accessdate=6 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121013030/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |archivedate=21 January 2015 }}</ref>\n*[[FIFA World Cup awards#Golden Ball|FIFA World Cup Bronze Ball]]: 1998<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/fifa-gb98.html|title=FIFA Awards - World Cup 1998 \"Golden Ball\"|publisher=RSSSF|author1=Jos\u00e9 Luis Pierrend|date=9 June 1999|accessdate=30 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[FIFA World Cup All-Star Team]]: 1998, 2006<ref name=\"MasterCard All-Star Team of the 1998 World Cup\"/>\n*[[European Sports Media#ESM Team of the Year|ESM Team of the Year]]: 1998\u201399, 2002\u201303<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/esm-xi.html|title=ESM XI|publisher=RSSSF|author1=Karel Stokkermans|date=14 March 2007|accessdate=29 November 2015}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA European Championship Teams of the Tournament|UEFA Euro Team of the Tournament]]: 2000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/finals/history/memories/newsid=1627525.html|title=UEFA Euro 2000 team of the tournament|website=uefa.com|publisher=UEFA|date=1 January 2011|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>\n*[[FIFA 100]]: 2004<ref name=\"Pele\">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/3533891.stm |title=Pele's list of the greatest |publisher=BBC Sport |date=4 March 2004 |accessdate=15 June 2013 }}</ref>\n*[[FIFPro World XI]]: 2006<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifpro.org/en/award-history/fifpro-world-xi-2005-2006|title=FIFPro World XI 2005/2006|publisher=FIFPro|date=20 December 2013|accessdate=9 June 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Troph\u00e9e d'honneur UNFP]]: 2009\n*[[\u00c9quipe type sp\u00e9ciale 20 ans des troph\u00e9es UNFP]]: 2011<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lfp.fr/corporate/article/eden-hazard-meilleur-joueur-de-ligue-1.htm|title=Eden Hazard meilleur joueur de Ligue 1|trans-title=Eden Hazard best Ligue 1 player|publisher=LFP|language=French|date=22 May 2011|accessdate=17 December 2015}}</ref>\n\n'''Orders'''\n*[[Chevalier of the L\u00e9gion d'honneur]]: 1998<ref name=Legion/>\n*[[Officier of the L\u00e9gion d'honneur]]: 2013<ref>{{cite journal |date=31 March 2013 |title=D\u00e9cret du 29 mars 2013 portant promotion et nomination |trans-title=Decree of 29 March 2013 on promotion and appointment |url=https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/affichTexte.do?cidTexte=JORFTEXT000027248227 |journal=Journal Officiel de la R\u00e9publique Fran\u00e7aise |volume=2013 |issue=0077 |page=5480 |id=PREX1307219D |accessdate=24 August 2019 |language=French}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{FIFA}}\n* {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120731025721/http://www.fcbarcelona.com/web/english/futbol/temporada_07-08/plantilla/jugadors/thuram.html |title=FC Barcelona player profile}}\n* {{LFP Ligue 1|lilian-thuram}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = France squads\n| bg = #002395\n| fg = white\n| bordercolor = #ED2939\n| list1 = \n{{France squad UEFA Euro 1996}}\n{{France squad 1998 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{France squad UEFA Euro 2000}}\n{{France squad 2002 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{France squad 2003 FIFA 